00:57:42.858 --> 00:57:44.038
the rare prevalence.

1007
00:57:46.278 --> 00:57:50.158
And also, colorectal cancer has very well characterized

1008
00:57:50.338 --> 00:57:54.218
risk factor profiles. So this has led to numerous

1009
00:57:54.278 --> 00:57:56.618
