1109
01:03:51.854 --> 01:03:55.634
for colonoscopy to better align with their

1110
01:03:56.114 --> 01:03:57.094
CRC risk.

1111
01:03:58.854 --> 01:04:02.754
So in the next few minutes, I just want to present some work that we have done

